ou、Luke Howard 和 A-Future。</p><p>与此同时，音乐节最近分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-shares-massive-shangri-la-area-line-up-for-2024-with-kneecap-bob-vylan-lambrini-girls-gorgon-city-and-more-3620049">香格里拉地区</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-to-debut-first-ever-south-asian-dedicated-stage-3620191">一个专门为南亚人才打造的新舞台的细节</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">在这里</a>查看迄今为止格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的完整阵容以及舞台划分。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-glastonbury-map-shows-changes-to-2024-festival-3759783">新格拉斯顿伯里 (New Glastonbury) 地图显示 2024 年音乐节的变化</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
乔·巴登否认前伴侣塔希里·何塞的虐待指控https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-budden-denies-abuse-allegation-from-video-vixen-tahiry-jose-love-and-hip-hop-new-york-3758957?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joe-budden-否认来自视频-vixen-tahiry-jose-love-and-hip-hop-new-york的滥用指控Kyann-Sian WilliamsMon, 27 May 2024 10:15:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3758957 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “塔希里，你是一个撒谎的、失败的淘金者”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-budden-denies-abuse-allegation-from-video-vixen-tahiry-jose-love-and-hip-hop-new-york-3758957">乔·布登 (Joe Budden) 否认前伴侣塔希里·何塞 (Tahiry José) 虐待指控的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/joe-budden-tahiry-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/joe-budden">乔·布登</a>回应了前伴侣塔希里·何塞指控他家庭暴力的评论。</p><p>巴登最近在<em>乔·巴登播客</em>上分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newly-published-surveillance-footage-reveals-diddy-attacking-cassie-3757408">2016 年吹牛老爹在洛杉矶一家酒店走廊袭击他的前女友兼签约人卡西·文图拉 (Cassie Ventura) 的病毒视频的</a>看法。</p><p>巴登说：“那段视频太恶心了，几乎让人无法忍受。”然后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-apologises-for-inexcusable-2016-video-allegedly-showing-him-attacking-ex-cassie-3757559">迪迪为自己在 2016 年央视视频中的行为所做的道歉是</a>“聋哑”、“半心半意的胡说八道”和“冒犯性”。 “我在视频中看到的内容——尽管很可怕——让我听过的任何可怕的事情都变得更加可信，这就是令人不舒服的地方，”巴登补充道。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">乔·巴登对迪迪发脾气。当他们在今天的播客中讨论吹牛老爹/卡西的视频时，称他为“撒谎的狗屎”。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/JoeBudden?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#JoeBudden</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Cassie?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Cassie</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/PDiddy?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PDiddy</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Puff?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Puff</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/JBP?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#JBP</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Podcast?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Podcast</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/JoeBuddenPodcast?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#JoeBuddenPodcast</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/CNN?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#CNN</a> <a href="https://t.co/TPxjsyvROq">pic.twitter.com/TPxjsyvROq</a></p><p> — 𝘋𝘌𝘕𝘕𝘐𝘚 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1f0-1f1ea.png" alt="🇰🇪" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> (@dennis_k_g) <a href="https://twitter.com/dennis_k_g/status/1793321646490898473?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 22 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7Rq3kksTyB/?img_index=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Shaderoom</em>的帖子</a>下，何塞回复了巴登对吹牛老爹镜头的评论：“[滚出这里]，谁？？？具有讽刺意味的。这太刺激了！！！我记得乔伊把我从楼梯上扔下来，把我拖回屋里，我不得不说服他让我走。用了几个小时！！！！</p><p> “这一切都让我出局了。太难看了。为卡西和其他所有正在经历或曾经经历过这种情况的女性感到抱歉。它太硬。”</p><p>巴登迅速回复，否认了针对他的指控。</p><p> “塔希里，你是一个撒谎的、失败的淘金者，虐待、针对和操纵了许多人，”他写道。 “在我之外，你缺乏自我认同，这就是为什么你在过去 15 年里拼命地想要依附于我。上次我见到你时，我从你那里购买了一张床垫，你很高兴你成功出售了，当时你很好。</p><p> “六年前《小星星》之后的那个晚上，你邀请我去你的新住处，那时你也很好。在<em>《Love &amp; Hip-Hop》的</em>最后一段时间里，你一直在我的身体上，并在这个过程中竭尽全力不尊重我儿子的母亲。我不得不要求制片人让你远离我们，就像你是癌症一样！！然而你仍然在网上轻视我的名字，因为……这是你的身份。”</p><p>他补充道：“我不跟你说话，也不谈论你，因为它的振动很低。你是一个低级戴克曼骗子，多年来一直在撒谎（你已经知道）。我祈祷你有一天能痊愈并继续前进。希望这是我们最后一次交流。为所有真正的受害者祈祷。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7R5B0iuAhJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" h