机后将她从床上拖了起来。 <a href="https://hiphopdx.com/news/id.57655/title.joe-budden-calls-tahiry-jose-a-cancerous-toxic-liar-says-she-used-to-beat-his-ass" target="_blank" rel="noopener">巴登当时否认了这一指控</a>，并告诉何塞：“你辱骂了！你曾经打过我的屁股！你扔狗屎，你打我，你踢我，你做了一大堆狗屎。”<em><br /></em></p><p>何塞否认有任何不当行为。</p><p>其他合作伙伴指控巴登身体虐待。 2011年，他的前女友<a href="https://www.xxlmag.com/esther-baxter-accuses-joe-budden-of-abuse-video/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">埃丝特·巴克斯特声称他所谓的暴力行为导致她流产</a>。这位“Pump It Up”说唱歌手<a href="https://www.xxlmag.com/joe-budden-denies-abuse-accusations/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在<em>Hot 97</em>上与 DJ Funkmaster Flex 的聊天中否认了这一说法</a>，他说：“郑重声明，我们要清楚的是，我从未打过 Esther。永远、永远、永远、永远。”</p><p>此外，<a href="https://thesource.com/2020/09/09/joe-budden-responds-to-cyn-santana-abuse-allegations/">巴登和前妻辛·桑塔纳之间的视频通话于 2022 年被泄露</a>，桑塔纳在视频通话中声称巴登追赶并拖拽她。当她通过电话告诉他这件事时，巴登否认了这些指控，并感到困惑。 “我拖你了？我把手放在你身上，把你拖到哪里去？我把你拖到哪里去了，Cyn？”巴登问道（根据<a href="https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/296748-cyn-santana-claims-joe-budden-physically-dragged-her-in-alleged-leaked-phone-call-news"><em>HotNewHipHop</em></a> ）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473196" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473196" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3473196" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty.jpg" alt="乔·巴登。照片来源：Shareif Ziyadat/Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joe-budden-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473196" cla